No. 640. Kentucky Distilleries and Warehouse Company, Petitioner, v. J. I. Blanton, Assignee, etc. March 18, 1907. Mr. William Marshall Bullitt, Mr. Alfred S. Austrian and Mr. Levy Mayer .for petitioner. Mr. Helm Bruce for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
